{"id":101048,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/朝鲜政权，真的有前途吗？！/","date":"2010-08-27T17:13:39Z","modified":"2010-09-29T18:21:46Z","title":"朝鲜政权，真的有前途吗？！","content":"<p><p><span>根据朝鲜劳动党中央政治局决定，<span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span>月上旬即将召开第七次劳动党代表大会。外界普遍认为，会上将正式确立金正日小儿子金正银的接班地位。在<span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span>年前召开的上一届党代会上，金正日当选为仅次于金日成的国家领导。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\">2009</span><span>年金正银已当选最高人民会议的代议员，从<span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span>年开始，<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span>日金正银的生日将成为朝鲜法定假日。今年<span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span>月初，朝鲜还破例召开了最高人民会议，任命张成泽为朝鲜国防委员会副委员长，使其成为“朝鲜第二号人物”，并更换了总理及多位副总理。<span lang=\"EN-US\">64</span>岁的张成泽是金正日的妹夫，被广泛看作是确保权力移交给金正银的最佳人士。</span></p>\n<p><span>金正日现年<span lang=\"EN-US\">69</span>岁，前两年因中风身体每况愈下。他从三个儿子金正男、金正哲和金正银中，挑选 ……</p>\n<p>……</span></p>\n<p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><strong><span><span></p>\n<p align=\"left\"><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></p>\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\">\n<p align=\"left\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n</p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></p>\n<p></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span><span><span><span></p>\n<p><span></p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n<p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n<p></span></p>\n<p></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n<p></span></p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>\n</p>